# Canonical source for BitMart rules.
# Keep one rule per line using DOMAIN-* / USER-AGENT / IP-CIDR syntax.
# Sources: BitMart iOS captures, official Python SDK (cloud_consts), CCXT, public DNS (1.1.1.1).
#
# Note: DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bitmart.com already covers most *.bitmart.com hosts.
# Important endpoints are still listed explicitly for readability and maintenance.

# --- Roots ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bitmart.site
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bitmart.io
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,snidefender.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,openc.pro

# --- Website / H5 / docs / status ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,www.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,h5.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,news.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,web3.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,affiliate.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,status.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,developer.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,developer-pro.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,support.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bitmart.zendesk.com

# --- Static / image CDN ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,static.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,static1.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,img.bitmart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bmstaticfiles.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com

# --- App / REST API (bitmart.com) ---
